    <item>
      <title>据 PTI 报道，莫迪盟友称，若无证据，他不会废除阿达尼交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/modi-s-ally-says-he-can-t-scrap-adani-deal-without-proof-pti</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据印度报业托拉斯报道，印度安得拉邦首席部长表示，除非有确凿证据证明阿达尼集团存在不法行为，否则该邦政府不会废除涉及阿达尼集团的购电协议，该协议是美国贿赂调查的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/modi-s-ally-says-he-can-t-scrap-adani-deal-without-proof-pti</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 07:07:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
